pLaunchControl

Class LedConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • pLaunchControl.LedConstants

  • public class LedConstants
extends java.lang.Object
    Hexadecimal values representing the possible combinations of color and intensity of pads in the MIDI controller. Values were extracted from the manufacturer documentation.
